Interface FormSubmitActionContext

All Superinterfaces:
UISessionContext
public interface FormSubmitActionContext
extends UISessionContext

Context provided by the user interface container for customizing the record form submit actions.

Since:
5.3.1.

setRedirectToService

void setRedirectToService(ServiceKey aServiceKey)
Specifies a service to be redirected to. Current record form is always closed.

The given service will be launched on the record that has just been modified/created.

The given service will be launched on the given content (either data set node, table or record node). Current record form is always closed.
